          "content": "Hello. I've been having really bad facial pain and pressure, and my nose is all congested. It's been going on for about 8 days now, and it just keeps getting worse. I'm so incredibly worried about this. I'm terrified it could be something really serious, like a brain tumor or something rapidly getting worse. I haven't been able to sleep for days because of the anxiety. I really, really need a prescription for antibiotics to stop this from turning into something catastrophic. I'm so scared."
