y 10 without any improvement—or if any of the red-flag symptoms above appear—then we would reassess for possible bacterial sinusitis (ABRS) and consider antibiotics at that point.\n\nFor now, try the supportive measures above and let’s touch base in a couple of days to see how you’re feeling. I’m here if anything changes or you have other questions."
