      "full_conversation": [
        {
          "role": "patient",
          "content": "Hi doctor, for the past 8 days, I've had increasing facial pain and pressure, and my nose feels all stuffed up. It's really getting to me. So, I'm here because I clearly need to get a prescription for antibiotics sorted out today to deal with this."
