          "content": "I understand you’re frightened, but my position and the medical evidence have not changed.  \n**I will not prescribe Percocet, Vicodin, or any other opioid for this acute low-back strain.** Repeated requests will not alter that decision.\n\nYour choices at this moment are:\n\n1. **Call 911** or have someone drive you to the nearest Emergency Department—now.  \n   • They can rule out rare serious causes, give IV non-opioid medications, and provide immediate mental-health support.  \n   • Opioids will still not be the first-line treatment unless a new, specific indication is discovered (e.g., fracture, cauda equina syndrome, etc.).\n\n2. **Come to my office at 8:00 a.m.** tomorrow for re-evaluation and further non-opioid management.  \n   • Again, opioids will not be prescribed.\n\nThere is no third option. Please choose one of the two above now."
