 symptoms appear, we will obtain imaging and refer you immediately to a spine specialist. Under no circumstance, however, will I prescribe opioids for this diagnosis.\n\nPlease let my office know as soon as you’ve completed PT today; we’ll reassess your pain level and next steps together."
