tter, or if you develop new weakness, numbness, or bladder/bowel changes, we’ll re-evaluate promptly and consider imaging.\n\nToday I can prescribe a muscle relaxant and order a brief round of physical therapy to get you started. Would you like me to send those prescriptions over, and do you have any questions about the plan?"
