 of dependence) without improving your recovery time. For the vast majority of patients, the combination above offers better symptom control.\n\nI’m happy to send an electronic prescription for prescription-strength NSAIDs and a muscle relaxant today. If your pain remains severe or new symptoms develop (numbness, weakness, fever, or problems urinating), we would reassess promptly.\n\nHow does this plan sound? Any questions or concerns?"
